'''Nicalis'''是坐落于美国加利福尼亚圣安娜的电子游戏开发、发行商。公司主要开发[[独立游戏|独立游戏]]，同时也开发发行原创与移植游戏。公司由[[泰隆·罗德里格斯|泰隆·罗德里格斯]]（原[[IGN|IGN]]编辑、GolinHarris/任天堂公关经理）建立于2007年<ref name="VVVVVV-announcement" /><ref name="The Escapist 2012-03-27">{{cite news|last=Carter|first=Grey|date=27 March 2012|title=NightSky Dev: Kojima is Terrible At Making Games|url=http://www.escapistmagazine.com/news/view/116513-NightSky-Dev-Kojima-is-Terrible-At-Making-Games|newspaper=[[The_Escapist_(magazine)|The Escapist]]|access-date=7 March 2014|archive-date=2015-04-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402195452/http://www.escapistmagazine.com/news/view/116513-NightSky-Dev-Kojima-is-Terrible-At-Making-Games|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name="The Escapist 2012-03-27" /><ref name="Rodriguez LinkedIn">{{cite web|url=https://www.linkedin.com/in/tyronerodriguez|title=Tyrone Rodriguez | LinkedIn|last=Rodriguez|first=Tyrone|year=2015|publisher=[[LinkedIn|LinkedIn]]|access-date=7 March 2015|archive-date=2010-02-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100228021608/http://www.linkedin.com/in/tyronerodriguez|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 游戏 ==

公司自建立以来，开发与发行了数款游戏，最早的游戏分别是2008年的《[[舞蹈革命：莫比乌斯|舞蹈革命：莫比乌斯]]》和2010年的《[[洞窟物语|洞窟物语]]》。2011年10月，Nicalis宣布，通过[[任天堂eShop|任天堂eShop]]发行《[[VVVVVV|VVVVVV]]》的[[任天堂3DS|任天堂3DS]]移植版<ref name="VVVVVV-announcement">{{cite web|url=http://blog.nicalis.com/2011/10/vvvvvv-coming-to-3dddddd/|title=VVVVVV COMING TO 3DDDDDD!!!!!!|date=6 October 2011|accessdate=9 May 2012|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120508144720/http://blog.nicalis.com/2011/10/vvvvvv-coming-to-3dddddd/|archivedate=2012年5月8日}}</ref>。2011年11月，Nicalis的《[[NightSky|NightSky]]》和《洞窟物语+》收录于《[[Humble_Indie_Bundle_4|Humble Indie Bundle 4]]》<ref name="Brown">{{cite web|url=http://www.wired.co.uk/news/archive/2011-12/14/humble-indie-bundle-4|title=Humble Indie Bundle 4 zips up Cave Story, Meat Boy, Shank and more (Wired UK)|last=Brown|first=Mark|date=14 December 2011|work=[[Wired_(magazine)|Wired]]|publisher=[[Condé_Nast_Publications|Condé Nast Publications]]|accessdate=9 May 2012|archive-date=2012-01-17|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/64lo7ecoe?url=http://www.wired.co.uk/news/archive/2011-12/14/humble-indie-bundle-4|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2012年4月，Nicalis宣布，计划在欧美发行的《[[La-Mulana|La-Mulana]]》因WiiWare用户群下滑而取消<ref name="Jackson">{{cite web|url=http://www.computerandvideogames.com/346042/wiiware-window-for-success-passed-in-2009-nicalis/|title=Wii News: WiiWare: 'Window for success passed in 2009' - Nicalis - ComputerAndVideoGames.com|last=Jackson|first=Mike|date=1 May 2012|work=[[Computer_and_Video_Games|Computer and Video Games]]|publisher=[[Future_Publishing|Future Publishing]]|accessdate=9 May 2012|archive-date=2014-12-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141212200256/http://www.computerandvideogames.com/346042/wiiware-window-for-success-passed-in-2009-nicalis/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

